# cibbot

Il bot Telegram di Cibbeâ„¢

### Setup

    bundle

### Running DB migrations

    bin/rake db:migrate

### Running tests

    bin/rake test

### Running the app

#### Prerequisites:

- Copy .env.example to .env
- Create your personal dev Telegram bot [see doc](https://core.telegram.org/bots#3-how-do-i-create-a-bot).
- Set your bot token on the .env file (TELEGRAM_TOKEN)

Start the app:

    bin/rackup

### Live testing with the telegram bot

Expose you local server to the Internet. For example with ngrok:

    ngrok http 9292

Set your host (for example https://e000a960.ngrok.io) on the .env file (WEBHOOK_URL)

(Re)start the app:

    bin/rackup


